he original sources of all religions should be taught, because with that we will find our similarities, not just our differences. I believe that if Mohammed, Buddha, Jesus, and Moses all got together they would be best of friends because the spiritual basis of all religions is something that builds unity.', 11977, 0), (458116, 'Let''s face it: Most of us don''t realize it, but we are failing our kids as reading role models. The best role models are in the home: brothers, fathers, grandfathers; mothers, sisters, grandmothers. Moms and dads, it''s important that your kids see you reading. Not just books - reading the newspaper is good, too.', 285, 0), (458117, 'I love being a woman. I love the sexiness we get to exude. But the best thing about being a woman is the power we have over men.', 67730, 0), (458118, 'When we do the best that we can, we never know what miracle is wrought in our life, or in the life of another.', 701, 0), (458119, 'The best doctors in the world are Doctor Diet, Doctor Quiet, and Doctor Merryman.', 995, 0), (458120, 'You get the best out of others when you get the best out of yourself.', 19497, 0), (458121, 'Do the best that you can in the place where you are, and be kind.', 72954, 0), (458122, 'My spiritual life is... sometimes I have access to it and sometimes I don''t. When I do have access to it, it''s usually a sense of my understanding what the best course of action or the best thing for me to do. By best, I mean when I have a real sense of doing the right thing and doing good for people and the connected universe of everybody.', 11414, 0), (458123, 'The best form of government is that which is most likely to prevent the greatest sum of evil.', 68738, 0), (458124, 'Do your best when no one is looking. If you do that, then you can be successful in anything that you put your mind to.', 72955, 0), (458125, 'I always prefer to believe the best of everybody, it saves so much trouble.', 843, 0), (458126, 'Man, being reasonable, must get drunk; 