INSERT INTO quotes (id, content, author_id, views) VALUES (458151, 'Never argue at the dinner table, for the one who is not hungry always gets the best of the argument.', 25969, 0), (458152, 'Laughter is the best medicine - unless you''re diabetic, then insulin comes pretty high on the list.', 72126, 0), (458153, 'I feel the best after a workout - I''m sweaty and exhausted, but it also gives me an energy I really like.', 71994, 0), (458154, 'I look at my grandparents and what they dealt with in the Japanese internment in Arizona. That sense of perseverance, of making the best out of an incredibly bad situation, has always been something I drew inspiration from. I always ask myself, ''What in the world do I have to complain about?''', 71493, 0), (458155, 'One way or another, we all have to find what best fosters the flowering of our humanity in this contemporary life, and dedicate ourselves to that.', 1123, 0), (458156, 'Education must provide the opportunities for self-fulfillment; it can at best provide a rich and challenging environment for the individual to explore, in his own way.', 1955, 0), (458157, 'In marketing I''ve seen only one strategy that can''t miss - and that is to market to your best customers first, your best prospects second and the rest of the world last.', 66842, 0), (458158, 'Real education should consist of drawing the goodness and the best out of our own students. What better books can there be than the book of humanity?', 28772, 0), (458159, 'I''m just trying to grow. That''s one thing I told myself is, ''Don''t worry about who people say is the best player.''', 1900, 0), (458160, 'The best way to impress a woman is to be the most honest you can.', 71096, 0), (458161, 'With the Union my best and dearest earthly hopes are entwined.', 72957, 0), (458162, 'Our best teachers do more than impart facts and figures - they inspire and encourage students and instill a true desire to learn. That''s a fine art in itself.', 72215, 0), (458163, 'There is always some kid who may be seeing me for the first time. I owe him my best.', 59511, 0), (458164, 'The night before I compete, I like to have steak. Meat is especially important for female athletes because it provides them with the nutrients they need to perform at their best.', 68093, 0), (458165, 'Here''s what I tell anybody and this is what I believe. The greatest gift we have is the gift of life. We understand that. That comes from our Creator. We''re given a body. Now you may not like it, but you can maximize that body the best it can be maximized.', 47904, 0), (458166, 'The point of living and of being an optimist is to be foolish enough to believe the best is yet to come.', 2206, 0), (458167, 'When I am traveling in a carriage, or walking after a good meal, or during the night when I cannot sleep; it is on such occasions that ideas flow best and most abundantly.', 611, 0), (458168, 'I''d say the best is when I was in Africa, I saw a hippo in a house. Someone had a pet hippo. And they''re meant to be one of the most dangerous animals on the planet, and they had one that was sort of just wandering in and out of their house, just sort of roaming about.', 1566, 0), (458169, 'Horror movies are the best date movies. There''s no wondering, ''When do I put my arm around her?''', 72958, 0), (458170, 'Above all, don''t fear difficult moments. The best comes from them.', 30658, 0), (458171, 'It''s not easy. I got lots of rejections when I first started out. If you want to write, you have to believe in yourself and not give up. You have to do your best to practice and get better.', 80, 0), (458172, 'In the animal kingdom, one of the keys to survival is to outwit your enemies. And when you''re surrounded by carnivores, one of the best strategies is to fade into the background and disappear.', 404, 0), (458173, 'I think laughter is the best medicine. If you can''t laugh at yourself, then you can''t laugh at life and the silliness of it all.', 67705, 0), (458174, 'Entrepreneurship is like a computer game in which you have to master every level before achieving success. Startups repeatedly stumble and have to go back to the drawing board. The best way to skip some levels and to increase the odds of survival is to learn from others who have already played the game.', 68872, 0), (458175, 'At United, there are great traditions, which you can''t buy in one or two years. They are created by victories. You need to prove again and again that you are better than the others. Manchester United have always done this, and are still doing it, so they are the best.', 5874, 0), (458176, 'The best art is realized when you can share the experience of making of it and not just the presentation of it, so that the audience is part of the creation and not just part of the consumption. Then it becomes much more full-bodied and robust.', 5054, 0), (458177, 'I focus on making sure I''m sharp, and it doesn''t matter who I am fighting. I need to perform at my best and try to elevate my game to the highest level I possibly can, so that is what I concentrate on doing.', 69352, 0), (458178, 'I''m at my best when people are depending on me. If it''s just on me and I don''t have nothing to do, I''m going to be lazy. On the football field, it''s every single day, every play, knowing that people are depending on me to make my play. That helps me elevate my game to another level.', 70002, 0), (458179, 'Do the best you can in every task, no matter how unimportant it may seem at the time. No one learns more about a problem than the person at the bottom.', 10500, 0), (458180, 'He who laughs most, learns best.', 8174, 0), (458181, 'A good book is the best of friends, the same today and forever.', 13498, 0), (458182, 'As simple as it sounds, we all must try to be the best person we can: by making the best choices, by making the most of the talents we''ve been given.', 65678, 0), (458183, 'Only mediocrity can be trusted to be always at its best.', 17074, 0), (458184, 'All the best people in life seem to like LINUX.', 4057, 0), (458185, 'Knowing that we can be loved exactly as we are gives us all the best opportunity for growing into the healthiest of people.', 167, 0), (458186, 'I am afraid we must make the world honest before we can honestly say to our children that honesty is the best policy.', 266, 0), (458187, 'My parents sacrificed so much for all of us. It makes me want to give back to them by being the best I can be.', 70503, 0), (458188, 'Michael Jordon may have been the best basketball player in history, but he couldn''t have won six NBA titles without a team.', 72959, 0), (458189, 'Sometimes you feel awkward being what you''re best at, you feel like you have to be something new.', 2519, 0), (458190, 'The best evaluation I can make of a player is to look in his eyes and see how scared they are.', 1813, 0), (458191, 'I think my best work is when I''m kind of in charge.', 2171, 0), (458192, 'I regarded finding I had a form of Alzheimer''s as an insult and decided to do my best to marshal any kind of forces I could against this wretched disease. I have posterior cortical atrophy or PCA. They say, rather ingenuously, that if you have Alzheimer''s it''s the best form of Alzheimer''s to have.', 195, 0), (458193, 'That''s what liberalism is all about, is promoting incompetence on the basis it''s fair, because people would be the best if they weren''t discriminated against.', 17531, 0), (458194, 'Write your story as it needs to be written. Write it honestly, and tell it as best you can. I''m not sure that there are any other rules. Not ones that matter.', 14, 0), (458195, 'Ideas percolate. Through natural selection, the best ones survive.', 72960, 0), (458196, 'I was a super-duper Tupac fan, and I realized later, when I became a huge Nas fan and a huge Eminem fan, I was drawn to the storytellers. They all told stories in different ways, but they were all like the best storytellers.', 60269, 0), (458197, 'Innovation and best practices can be sown throughout an organization - but only when they fall on fertile ground.', 35133, 0), (458198, 'The best clubs in the world are always the clubs where you have a variety of people. Like, you have the crazy people, you have the nicely dressed people, you have the office people, you have the regular guys - that makes it fun.', 69210, 0), (458199, 'Never die easy. Why run out of bounds and die easy? Make that linebacker pay. It carries into all facets of your life. It''s okay to lose, to die, but don''t die without trying, without giving it your best.', 2100, 0), (458200, 'My mind has been both my best friend and my worst enemy.', 72961, 0);
INSERT INTO quotes (id, content, author_id, views) VALUES (458201, 'Friends always ask me what the best Indian restaurant in L.A. is. I''m like, ''I don''t know, dude. I have an app on my iPhone for that.''', 72694, 0), (458202, 'My motto is to do everything absolutely flat out and to the best of your ability.', 72078, 0), (458203, 'Cognitive psychology has shown that the mind best understands facts when they are woven into a conceptual fabric, such as a narrative, mental map, or intuitive theory. Disconnected facts in the mind are like unlinked pages on the Web: They might as well not exist.', 3432, 0), (458204, 'I was first in line for the iPhone, but I''m not a fanboy of any company - I''m in favor of anything that''s best of breed.', 66710, 0), (458205, 'Goodness is beauty in the best estate.', 6093, 0), (458206, 'The best way out of a difficulty is through it.', 1122, 0), (458207, 'I have made the choices that work best for me. I know I cannot please everyone, and that''s fine.', 67063, 0), (458208, 'Nobody who ever gave his best regretted it.', 70549, 0), (458209, 'People who lean on logic and philosophy and rational exposition end by starving the best part of the mind.', 62867, 0), (458210, 'I believe that a simple and unassuming manner of life is best for everyone, best both for the body and the mind.', 104, 0), (458211, 'Expect the best. Prepare for the worst. Capitalize on what comes.', 1692, 0), (458212, 'When the world is running down, you make the best of what''s still around.', 9151, 0), (458213, 'Just live life. That''s the best way to learn how to act. Just live.', 72962, 0), (458214, 'Best thing that''s happened this year? Maybe Hostel. It was a great experience. I loved it.', 72963, 0), (458215, 'The President of the United States should strive to be always mindful of the fact that he serves his party best who serves his country best.', 37393, 0), (458216, 'Watching a good actor is the best way to learn.', 72964, 0), (458217, 'I never understand when people say, ''School days are the best of your life.'' So it''s all downhill from 16? How depressing.', 72965, 0), (458218, 'There''s a tipping point that happens with soccer in which you just kinda get it. I was drawn to it because the best soccer teams play similarly to my favorite basketball teams - like the eighties Lakers or eighties Celtics - teams that emphasized teamwork over individualism and relied on passing as their biggest ongoing edge.', 69712, 0), (458219, 'Nobody''s life is a bed of roses. We all have crosses to bear, and we all just do our best. I would never claim to have the worst situation. There are many widows, and many people dying of AIDS, many people killed in Lebanon, people starving all over the planet. So we have to count our lucky stars.', 1121, 0), (458220, 'By taking to the road, we free ourselves of baggage, both physical and psychological. We walk back to our original condition, to our best selves.', 18322, 0), (458221, 'The best way to forget ones self is to look at the world with attention and love.', 47736, 0), (458222, 'Your purpose is to make your audience see what you saw, hear what you heard, feel what you felt. Relevant detail, couched in concrete, colorful language, is the best way to recreate the incident as it happened and to picture it for the audience.', 1005, 0), (458223, 'So if diva means giving your best, then yes, I guess I am a diva.', 66236, 0), (458224, 'There would be no debate about who was the best footballer the world had ever seen - me or Pele. Everyone would say me.', 72935, 0), (458225, 'Participation, I think, or one of the best methods of educating.', 72966, 0), (458226, 'I''m not the best singer, but I like the way I sing my songs.', 71075, 0), (458227, 'Soap and water and common sense are the best disinfectants.', 3668, 0), (458228, 'I try my best, but at the same time, I try not to let being out with someone affect my everyday life. Like, if I want to go out and grab a smoothie with a friend who''s a male, I''m not gonna let the paparazzi stop me from doing that and living my life and just being a normal person.', 68261, 0), (458229, 'If I am a cup maker, I''m interested in making the best cup I possibly can. My effort goes into that cup, not what people think about it.', 5253, 0), (458230, 'That is the difference between good teachers and great teachers: good teachers make the best of a pupil''s means great teachers foresee a pupil''s ends.', 19739, 0), (458231, 'The corruption of the best things gives rise to the worst.', 2498, 0), (458232, 'I''ve always been a pretty candid person. I''m not a very secretive person I''m not a very discreet person. One of my best friends once described me as pathologically indiscreet.', 9309, 0), (458233, 'Life is about not knowing, having to change, taking the moment and making the best of it, without knowing what''s going to happen next.', 993, 0), (458234, 'I started getting Twitter followers after I started doing press for ''Fargo.'' One of my best friends from college is a librarian, and she started tracking after each interview how many Twitter followers I got. She and her librarian friends were like, ''We''re going to make a graph.'' And I was like, ''Alright, nerds.''', 72967, 0), (458235, 'We have to face the fact that countries are going to lose jobs to robotics. The only question that needs to be answered is which country will create and own the best robotic technology and have the infrastructure necessary to enable it.', 35063, 0), (458236, 'If I stopped writing and being at my piano, I wouldn''t know how to live. It''s your best friend.', 72968, 0), (458237, 'To be a utilitarian means that you judge actions as right or wrong in accordance with whether they have good consequences. So you try to do what will have the best consequences for all of those affected.', 2537, 0), (458238, 'My job is to play quarterback, and I''m going to do that the best way I know how, because I owe that to my teammates regardless of who is out there on the field with me.', 66949, 0), (458239, 'You had better live your best and act your best and think your best today for today is the sure preparation for tomorrow and all the other tomorrows that follow.', 34936, 0), (458240, 'It pays to get drunk with the best people.', 63346, 0), (458241, 'Set up another case bartender! The best thing for a case of nerves is a case of Scotch.', 2165, 0), (458242, 'My best vacation memory is getting barreled at the beach in Hawaii.', 67739, 0), (458243, 'For every athlete, it is very important to be able to engage in their favorite thing, give all the best in training, performing in competitions, defending the honor of the motherland.', 49653, 0), (458244, 'Even between the best of friends, mistakes and misunderstandings can happen.', 72969, 0), (458245, 'I think it''s very hard to find a good friend. That''s why I''m so lucky to have two sisters, because they''re my best friends, and they have to be with me forever. They''re stuck with me.', 69776, 0), (458246, 'Likewise, there is no evidence that texting teaches people to spell badly: rather, research shows that those kids who text frequently are more likely to be the most literate and the best spellers, because you have to know how to manipulate language.', 42008, 0), (458247, 'I have won many awards and I am very happy about this, but I am not the best player in the world.', 70543, 0), (458248, 'A high-powered, successful woman doesn''t necessarily have the same support behind her that a man in that position would. Plus, she''s expected to be a domestic goddess, as well as the best wife, mother, friend, and lover. But it''s not just in politics: you see it in acting, too, and in journalism.', 72970, 0), (458249, 'Since scarcity is the basic economic problem, if it does not exist then there is no reason for my economics course. Devoting time to the study of how people use limited resources to fulfill unlimited wants and needs should help us to discover how to best utilize the resources we have at our disposal.', 72971, 0), (458250, 'Sometimes the best way to learn something is by doing it wrong and looking at what you did.', 14, 0);
INSERT INTO quotes (id, content, author_id, views) VALUES (458251, 'We can use decision-making to choose the habits we want to form, use willpower to get the habit started, then - and this is the best part - we can allow the extraordinary power of habit to take over. At that point, we''re free from the need to decide and the need to use willpower.', 3243, 0), (458252, 'One of the best predictors of policy around is Thomas Ferguson''s investment theory of politics, as he calls it - very outstanding political economist - which essentially - I mean, to say it in a sentence, he describes elections as occasions in which groups of investors coalesce and invest to control the state.', 1955, 0), (458253, 'I have never - I have never let go of my childhood contacts. My best friends from childhood are still my best friends.', 72972, 0), (458254, 'My best birth control now is just to leave the lights on.', 17330, 0), (458255, 'Infinite striving to be the best is man''s duty it is its own reward. Everything else is in God''s hands.', 32, 0), (458256, 'If someone were to put a proposition before men bidding them choose, after examination, the best customs in the world, each nation would certainly select its own.', 1863, 0), (458257, 'That was the best ice cream soda I ever tasted.', 72973, 0), (458258, 'Every single job is a challenge. You are walking into a new set, a new character, creating a world and trying to get comfortable to do your best work.', 2287, 0), (458259, 'When we believe the best of people, we let go of each thing they do that is hurtful to us. And we choose to think things like, ''I don''t believe they meant to hurt me.'' ''Maybe they''re having a bad day or don''t feel well.'' ''They probably don''t even realize how they sound.''', 1206, 0), (458260, 'I consider my ability to arouse enthusiasm among men the greatest asset I possess. The way to develop the best that is in a man is by appreciation and encouragement.', 63087, 0), (458261, 'In life, try your best to do the right thing. Have fun while you''re alive. Take advantage of every asset you have. Don''t take anything for granted.', 72974, 0), (458262, 'When you''re onstage and the audience is smiling and singing and bopping along and you''re all on the same level, it''s the best feeling in the world. It may sound dumb and corny to say it, but it''s like pure love.', 68442, 0), (458263, 'Learn to invest in the best quality you can afford and wear pieces in different ways.', 68379, 0), (458264, 'The best description of the Old Testament that I heard was that it starts out as mythology, then it becomes legend, then it becomes history. In the mythological period - there is a distinct mythological period in the Old Testament, where the time spans are impossible and really just imagined.', 28896, 0), (458265, 'My philosophy is that not only are you responsible for your life, but doing the best at this moment puts you I the best place for the next moment.', 588, 0), (458266, 'The best move you can make in negotiation is to think of an incentive the other person hasn''t even thought of - and then meet it.', 57633, 0), (458267, 'I have never gone on a real trip, never taken a holiday. The best holiday for me is spent in my workshops when nearly everybody else is on vacation.', 71388, 0), (458268, 'I''ve learned that I am allowed to say what I like and what I don''t like. And I''ve learned that I have to be professional and not be everyone''s best friend.', 38226, 0), (458269, 'I''m not afraid of working hard at anything, whatever it is. I just always want to be the best that I can.', 47135, 0), (458270, 'I''m just doing the best I can now to keep this going... trying to grow up and remain young at the same time.', 71410, 0), (458271, 'In football, it''s the job of the player to play, the coach to coach, the official to officiate. Each guy is charged with upholding his end, nothing more. In golf, the player, coach and official are rolled into one, and they overlap completely. Golf really is the best microcosm of life - or at least the way life should be.', 2081, 0), (458272, 'Working with some of the best makeup artists has taught me a lot of amazing tricks to making me feel more confident, and I can''t wait to share them with you guys.', 66658, 0), (458273, 'I don''t plan to take a formal, cold approach with my children, but I expect a lot. I don''t want my children to view me as their best friend. I want to be their mom.', 26172, 0), (458274, 'The best substitute for experience is being sixteen.', 72975, 0), (458275, 'Perhaps it sounds ridiculous, but the best thing that young filmmakers should do is to get hold of a camera and some film and make a movie of any kind at all.', 7875, 0), (458276, 'I''ve found the best way is to not be scared of the attention but to be grateful for it and open to it. It makes my days better rather than being annoyed that people want my attention.', 72976, 0), (458277, 'Fit no stereotypes. Don''t chase the latest management fads. The situation dictates which approach best accomplishes the team''s mission.', 1749, 0), (458278, 'I think one of the reasons that we like conspiracy theories is I think that we like to feel like there is a group of people who are so smart and powerful that they can pull the wool over an entire country or in fact even an entire world''s eyes. That certainly makes us feel like somehow we''re protected, even if it''s not in our best interest.', 72977, 0), (458279, 'You know I need that cockiness, the self-belief, arrogance, swagger, whatever you want to call it, I need that on the golf course to bring the best out of myself. So you know once I leave the golf course, you know that all gets left there.', 72004, 0), (458280, 'I haven''t personally experienced bullying, but when I was in high school, I had a best friend who became a bully. I took a stand and took it upon myself to separate from her. I couldn''t be associated with her because it wasn''t the type of person I wanted to be.', 71969, 0), (458281, 'The bold adventurer succeeds the best.', 782, 0), (458282, 'The best solutions are often simple, yet unexpected.', 71962, 0), (458283, 'The best of life is to embark on an adventure with a woman interested in having an adventure with you.', 72978, 0), (458284, 'Hockey lends itself to special events, including the Olympic competition: a glorious tournament of the best players in the world, putting on their national jerseys and playing on big rinks with no-goon Olympic rules and referee enforcement.', 67719, 0), (458285, 'Experience taught me a few things. One is to listen to your gut, no matter how good something sounds on paper. The second is that you''re generally better off sticking with what you know. And the third is that sometimes your best investments are the ones you don''t make.', 64643, 0), (458286, 'We''re all flawed, but basically, effective managers are people whose flaws are not fatal under the circumstances. Maybe the best managers are simply ordinary, healthy people who aren''t too screwed up.', 59359, 0), (458287, 'I will do my best. That is all I can do. I ask for your help - and God''s.', 1763, 0), (458288, 'Just the fact that a thousand people in front of me were ready to hear me sing was one of the best feelings I can think of.', 69236, 0), (458289, 'The prizes go to those who meet emergencies successfully. And the way to meet emergencies is to do each daily task the best we can.', 5249, 0), (458290, 'I was blessed with certain gifts and talents and God gave them to me to be the best person I can be and to have a positive impact on other people.', 72979, 0), (458291, 'My mother and I are more than best friends; we are partners in crime. After she and my father, Quincy Jones, separated when I was 10 years old, my sister, Kidada, who was 12, went to live with our dad, and I stayed with my mother.', 18940, 0), (458292, 'When I do interviews, I enter them with an open mind and try to answer the questions the best I can.', 71398, 0), (458293, 'The best thing I have is the knife from Fatal Attraction. I hung it in my kitchen. It''s my way of saying, Don''t mess with me.', 24425, 0), (458294, 'The best effort of a fine person is felt after we have left their presence.', 760, 0), (458295, 'In politics, strangely enough, the best way to play your cards is to lay them face upwards on the table.', 3173, 0), (458296, 'The best things and best people rise out of their separateness I''m against a homogenized society because I want the cream to rise.', 35, 0), (458297, 'Let America first praise mediocrity even, in her children, before she praises... the best excellence in the children of any other land.', 2584, 0), (458298, 'Prosperity is the best protector of principle.', 286, 0), (458299, 'I think the best thing I can do is to be a distraction. A husband lives and breathes his work all day long. If he comes home to more table thumping, how can the poor man ever relax?', 27555, 0), (458300, 'Personally, I think the best motto for an educational establishment is: ''Or Would You Rather Be a Mule?''', 195, 0);
