f ourselves and who we are as New Yorkers and Americans if we said no to a mosque in lower Manhattan.', 67699, 0), (458314, 'The best career advice to give to the young is, ''Find out what you like doing best and get someone to pay you for doing it.''', 62901, 0), (458315, 'Maria is the best reason to come home.', 12194, 0), (458316, 'The abduction of a child is a tragedy. No one can fully understand or appreciate what a parent goes through at such a time, unless they have faced a similar tragedy. Every parent responds differently. Each parent copes with this nightmare in the best way he or she knows how.', 72980, 0), (458317, 'Townes Van Zandt is the best songwriter in the whole world, and I''ll stand on Bob Dylan''s coffee table in my cowboy boots and say that.', 55413, 0), (458318, 'The best prophet of the future is the past.', 62558, 0), (458319, 'I just need to know that I did the very best I could and that I was true to myself.', 68285, 0), (458320, 'Competition brings out the best in products and the worst in people.', 32896, 0), (458321, 'It is best to act with confidence, no matter how little right you have to it.', 1991, 0), (458322, 'One cannot develop taste from what is of average quality but only from the very best.', 282, 0), (458323, 'I believe in Las Vegas. I think its best days are ahead of it. But I''m afraid to do anything in the current political environment in the United States.', 67055, 0), (458324, 'If I have a rap album I''m dropping, then I want it to be the best rap album.', 2080, 0), (458325, 'Wishful thinking is not idealism. It is self-indulgence at best and self-exaltation at worst. In either case, it is usually at the expense of others. In other words, it is the opposite of idealism.', 2589, 0), (458326, 'Accept who you are and try and make the best of that.', 66784, 0), (458327, 'I want to deal with what''s in front of me now to the best of my abilities, and sometimes that''s not very good. But a lot of the days it is really great.', 