o the people who are on the front line.', 5248, 0), (458590, 'People tend to dwell more on negative things than on good things. So the mind then becomes obsessed with negative things, with judgments, guilt and anxiety produced by thoughts about the future and so on.', 378, 0), (458591, 'As any doctor can tell you, the most crucial step toward healing is having the right diagnosis. If the disease is precisely identified, a good resolution is far more likely. Conversely, a bad diagnosis usually means a bad outcome, no matter how skilled the physician.', 5974, 0), (458592, 'There is no such thing as bad weather, only different kinds of good weather.', 485, 0), (458593, 'Well, there''s nothing better than putting your feet up on a Sunday afternoon and grabbing a good book.', 69721, 0), (458594, 'Sleeping is like meditation: it''s good to rest the body but also to shut the mind down for a bit.', 68663, 0), (458595, 'Resilience is accepting your new reality, even if it''s less good than the one you had before.', 18433, 0), (458596, 'It takes more than just a good looking body. You''ve got to have the heart and soul to go with it.', 1328, 0), (458597, 'All good things which exist are the fruits of originality.', 1880, 0), (458598, 'The evil that men do lives after them the good is oft interred with their bones.', 13, 0), (458599, 'Our higher education system is one of the things that makes America exceptional. There''s no place else that has the assets we do when it comes to higher education. People from all over the world aspire to come here and study here. And that is a good thing.', 1693, 0), (458600, 'We all have the duty to do good.', 6248, 0);
INSERT INTO quotes (id, content, author_id, views) VALUES (458601, 'No matter what has happened to you in the past or what is going on in your life right now, it has no power to keep you from having an amazingly good future if you will walk by faith in God. God loves you! He wants you to live with victory over sin so you can possess His promises for your life today!', 1206, 0), (458602, 'Thanksgiving Day is a good day to recommit our energies to giving thanks and just giving.', 64661, 0), (458603, 'I wake up every day and I think, ''I''m breathing! It''s a good day.''', 667, 0), (458604, 'Good friends don''t have to visit each other every day.', 73003, 0), (458605, 'I tried to drown my sorrows, but the bastards learned how to swim, and now I am overwhelmed by this decent and good feeling.', 1759, 0), (458606, 'Doing good holds the power to transform us on the inside, and then ripple out in ever-expanding circles that positively impact the world at large.', 66578, 0), (458607, 'You''re only as good as your last haircut.', 1437, 0), (458608, 'A good mustache makes a man for many reasons.', 69354, 0), (458609, 'If I play a villain, I try to find his lightness and his good side. And if I play a hero or a good guy, I''ll try to find his darkness or his flaws. Because I don''t believe in good and evil. I believe in grays.', 68236, 0), (458610, 'I''m very happy with my life. I am what I am. I don''t worry about anything that I can''t control. That''s a really good lesson in life.', 68217, 0), (458611, 'You have good days, you have bad days. But the main thing is to grow mentally.', 67644, 0), (458612, 'Sometimes we look back and 10 years from now we think, ''Boy, those were great old days.'' Well, you know, we''re living in the good old days.', 3956, 0), (458613, 'A good fragrance should have a certain personality that makes people identify the scent with you.', 67847, 0), (458614, 'The true measure of a man is how he treats someone who can do him absolutely no good.', 208