 I can go and how good I can be, whether it''s in the classroom or on the football field.', 73010, 0), (458716, 'Laughter is an important part of a good relationship. It''s an immense achievement when you can move from your thinking that your partner is merely an idiot to thinking that they are that wonderfully complex thing called a loveable idiot. And often that means having a little bit of a sense of humour about their flaws.', 639, 0), (458717, 'The reading of all good books is like a conversation with the finest minds of past centuries.', 2272, 0), (458718, 'A magnetic personality doesn''t necessarily indicate a good heart.', 10905, 0), (458719, 'My advice to anybody, including myself, is if you''re going through a bad period, and you just can''t see the world''s on your shoulders and no day is a good day, you''re missing the whole point of the experience. And that''s something dogs know from the moment they come bounding up to you as a puppy.', 33965, 0), (458720, 'Never call an accountant a credit to his profession a good accountant is a debit to his profession.', 46113, 0), (458721, 'There''s no regret. You can''t regret. I mean, I''ve felt regret but I''ve also refused to allow regret to sow a seed and live in me because I don''t believe it. You feel it, it''s like guilt, it''s like jealousy, it''s like all those horrible things. You''ve just got to snip them and get them out, because they''re no good.', 70651, 0), (458722, 'Everything has become so easy. It''s great that it''s at your fingertips, but I miss those good old days. And we''re connected, but it can be very alienating. There is this distance between all of us because we''re speaking to each other through cameras and monitors and icons and Emojis.', 71113, 0), (458723, 'If you think people are inherently good, you get rid of the police for 24 hours - see what happens.', 35699, 0), (458724, 'A good director creates an environment, which gives the actor the encouragement to fly.', 26931, 0), (458725, 'Good seasons start with good beginnings.', 65137, 0), (458726, 'Jealousy is both reasonable and belongs to reasonable men, while envy is base and belongs to the base, for the one makes himself get good things by jealousy, while the other does not allow his neighbour to have them through envy.', 1116, 0), (458727, 'I have found little that is ''good'' about human beings on the whole. In my experience most of them are trash, no matter whether they publicly subscribe to this or that ethical doctrine or to none at all. That is something that you cannot say aloud, or perhaps even think.', 555, 0), (458728, 'Reading a book about management isn''t going to make you a good manager any more than a book about guitar will make you a good guitarist, but it can get you thinking about the most important concepts.', 69857, 0), (458729, 'A liar should have a good memory.', 63010, 0), (458730, 'Looking beautiful isn''t just about what you apply on your face. It''s the little things you do that matter. A combination of a good diet, exercise, healthy habits, discipline, dancing etc. is what my beauty routine consists of. Also, I have no bad habits; I don''t drink or smoke. All these contribute to me being fit and looking good.', 71520, 0), (458731, 'True intuitive expertise is learned from prolonged experience with good feedback on mistakes.', 6017, 0), (458732, 'When you have a daughter, you want to protect her from the things that I''ve seen out there, you know, the things that''s out there that ain''t good for her. It''s a crazy world we live in.', 66586, 0), (458733, 'A good example is far better than a good precept.', 3200, 0), (458734, 'Dedicate yourself to the good you deserve and desire for yourself. Give yourself peace of mind. You deserve to be happy. You deserve delight.', 68089, 0), (458735, 'I think one of the most important things in a relationship is caring for your significant other through good times and bad.', 67879, 0), (458736, 'People are always good company when they are doing what they really enjoy.', 4111, 0), (458737, 'Life is not a matter of holding good cards, but sometimes, playing a poor hand well.', 1094, 0), (458738, 'I feel like if you''re a really good human being, you can try to find something beautiful in every single person, no matter what.', 47, 0), (458739, 'Good design begins with honesty, asks tough questions, comes from collaboration and from trusting your intuition.', 73011, 0), (458740, 'When you begin to worry, go find something to do. Get busy being a blessing to someone; do something fruitful. Talking about your problem or sitting alone, thinking about it, does no good; it serves only to make you miserable. Above all else, remember that worrying is totally useless. Worrying will not solve your problem.', 1206, 0), (458741, 'I actually think that the most efficacious way of making a difference is to lead by example, and doing random acts of kindness is setting a very good example of how to behave in the world.', 19755, 0), (458742, 'For me, life is about experience and being a good person.', 73012, 0), (458743, 'Fun is good.', 3, 0), (458744, 'What do I think of Western civilization? I think it would be a very good idea.', 32, 0), (458745, 'People change over the years, and that changes situations for good and for bad.', 7610, 0), (458746, 'Less is only more where more is no good.', 1836, 0), (458747, 'They didn''t want it good, they wanted it Wednesday.', 17, 0), (458748, 'Being a good leader requires remembering that you''re there for a reason, and the reason certainly isn''t to have your way. High-integrity leaders not only welcome questioning and criticism - they insist on it.', 68087, 0), (458749, 'No matter how busy I get or how much pressure is on my shoulders, a good workout makes me feel at ease. I come off the treadmill feeling relaxed, full of joy and with a sense of perspective over the issues on my plate.', 1172, 0), (458750, 'I am in politics because of the conflict between good and 