INSERT INTO quotes (id, content, author_id, views) VALUES (458751, 'Rather than dividing the world between good and evil, the Left divided the world in terms of economics. Economic classes, not moral values, explained human behavior. Therefore, to cite a common example, poverty, not one''s moral value system, or lack of it, caused crime.', 4608, 0), (458752, 'I am confident that, in the end, common sense and justice will prevail. I''m an optimist, brought up on the belief that if you wait to the end of the story, you get to see the good people live happily ever after.', 61043, 0), (458753, 'None of Us is as Good as All of Us.', 37739, 0), (458754, 'Associate yourself with people of good quality, for it is better to be alone than in bad company.', 5998, 0), (458755, 'I am like the sick sheep that strays from the rest of the flock. Unless the Good Shepherd takes me on His shoulders and carries me back to His fold, my steps will falter, and in the very effort of rising, my feet will give way.', 62829, 0), (458756, 'When you have a dark side, nothing is ever as good as it seems.', 67650, 0), (458757, 'Twice and thrice over, as they say, good is it to repeat and review what is good.', 51, 0), (458758, 'I think life is a matter of choices and that wherever we are, good or bad, is because of choices we make.', 2081, 0), (458759, 'The good thing about flying solo is it''s never boring.', 69819, 0), (458760, 'There are going to be good times and bad times, but lighten up.', 12497, 0), (458761, 'There''s nothing wrong with being a loser, it just depends on how good you are at it.', 52296, 0), (458762, 'Destiny is a good thing to accept when it''s going your way. When it isn''t, don''t call it destiny; call it injustice, treachery, or simple bad luck.', 1320, 0), (458763, 'Great champions have an enormous sense of pride. The people who excel are those who are driven to show the world and prove to themselves just how good they are.', 65562, 0), (458764, 'Just knowing you don''t have the answers is a recipe for humility, openness, acceptance, forgiveness, and an eagerness to learn - and those are all good things.', 12496, 0), (458765, 'When you realize who the good people are in your life, you''re so lucky.', 67671, 0), (458766, 'I can live for two months on a good compliment.', 286, 0), (458767, 'There is a fine line between censorship and good taste and moral responsibility.', 5194, 0), (458768, 'Animals praise a good day, a good hunt. They praise rain if they''re thirsty. That''s prayer. They don''t live an unconscious life, they simply have no language to talk about these things. But they are grateful for the good things that come along.', 130, 0), (458769, 'If a great outfit gets you one step closer to feeling good about yourself, then it''s worth every penny.', 66619, 0), (458770, 'I think sometimes in life we want to ignore the problems of society and just think about the good. I believe in positive thinking and affirmative living, I also think it''s really important to remember all of our disenfranchised members of society.', 37611, 0), (458771, 'The fact is that people are good, Give people affection and security, and they will give affection and be secure in their feelings and their behavior.', 62519, 0), (458772, 'A hard beginning maketh a good ending.', 41914, 0), (458773, 'Good character consists of recognizing the selfishness that inheres in each of us and trying to balance it against the altruism to which we should all aspire. It is a difficult balance to strike, but no definition of goodness can be complete without it.', 17810, 0), (458774, 'God is good for everybody. The sun shines on good people and bad people, and it rains on both, too. God doesn''t choose rain only for bad people.', 67646, 0), (458775, 'Luck is everything... My good luck in life was to be a really frightened person. I''m fortunate to be a coward, to have a low threshold of fear, because a hero couldn''t make a good suspense film.', 2186, 0), (458776, 'Be not simply good - be good for something.', 1049, 0), (458777, 'The more we come out and do good to others, the more our hearts will be purified, and God will be in them.', 1838, 0), (458778, 'The definition of a good mathematical problem is the mathematics it generates rather than the problem itself.', 73013, 0), (458779, 'To be doing good deeds is man''s most glorious task.', 139, 0), (458780, 'You''ll find boredom where there is the absence of a good idea.', 1888, 0), (458781, 'I believe, I believe every day is a good day when you paint.', 1710, 0), (458782, 'A long healthy life is no accident. It begins with good genes, but it also depends on good habits.', 4994, 0), (458783, 'Well, you need the villain. If you don''t have a villain, the good guy can stay home.', 73014, 0), (458784, 'If you are the person who gets the lion''s share of attention in good times, guess what: you get the lion''s share of attention in bad times.', 68504, 0), (458785, 'No man is so foolish but he may sometimes give another good counsel, and no man so wise that he may not easily err if he takes no other counsel than his own. He that is taught only by himself has a fool for a master.', 126, 0), (458786, 'Photography is like a moment, an instant. You need a half-second to get the photo. So it''s good to capture people when they are themselves.', 70526, 0), (458787, 'The good inside of all of us is wrapped in a layer of apathy, and we forget how much potential we have within us, in each and every one of us, to change the world for the better for ourselves and our children, and thus to bring about oneness.', 66578, 0), (458788, 'I went further on less talent than anyone, but I was a damned good entertainer.', 23263, 0), (458789, 'You punch me, I punch back. I do not believe it''s good for one''s self-respect to be a punching bag.', 67486, 0), (458790, 'People don''t want to go to the dump and have a picnic, they want to go out to a beautiful place and enjoy their day. And so I think our job is to try to take the environment, take what the good Lord has given us, and expand upon it or enhance it, without destroying it.', 64787, 0), (458791, 'I don''t judge others. I say if you feel good with what you''re doing, let your freak flag fly.', 4816, 0), (458792, 'Jogging is very beneficial. It''s good for your legs and your feet. It''s also very good for the ground. If makes it feel needed.', 151, 0), (458793, 'Shallow understanding from people of good will is more frustrating than absolute misunderstanding from people of ill will.', 21767, 0), (458794, 'This is important: to get to know people, listen, expand the circle of ideas. The world is crisscrossed by roads that come closer together and move apart, but the important thing is that they lead towards the Good.', 6248, 0), (458795, 'The underbelly of the human psyche, what is often referred to as our dark side, is the origin of every act of self-sabotage. Birthed out of shame, fear, and denial, it misdirects our good intentions and drives us to unthinkable acts of self-destruction and not-so-unbelievable acts of self-sabotage.', 5671, 0), (458796, 'Of all that is good, sublimity is supreme. Succeeding is the coming together of all that is beautiful. Furtherance is the agreement of all that is just. Perseverance is the foundation of all actions.', 15, 0), (458797, 'Old things are always in good repute, present things in disfavor.', 3582, 0), (458798, 'Life is good when we think it''s good. Life is bad when we don''t think.', 67402, 0), (458799, 'Without your health, you''ve got nothing going on. I thank God every day for good health.', 66686, 0), (458800, 'When you train seven days a week, you need good scenery to inspire you.', 71098, 0);
INSERT INTO quotes (id, content, author_id, views) VALUES (458801, 'As you are not yet married, and as marriage is the fundamental state of life as well as the unity of the commonwealth, make up your mind whether you are called to this state. If you make up your mind to marry, do not marry merely a good wife: marry a good mother to your children.', 7316, 0), (458802, 'The funny thing is, I''m so used to not caring what anyone says, good or bad, that unfortunately even when people say good things... I wish it made me feel good, but it doesn''t.', 67097, 0), (458803, 'I wouldn''t say that I am one of the greatest dancers, but I am really quite good at what I do.', 47, 0), (458804, 'The past is our definition. We may strive with good reason to escape it, or to escape what is bad in it. But we will escape it only by adding something better to it.', 1152, 0), (458805, 'The good and the wise lead quiet lives.', 542, 0), (458806, 'It''s good to shut up sometimes.', 22725, 0), (458807, 'When one has the feeling of dislike for evil, when one feels tranquil, one finds pleasure in listening to good teachings; when one has these feelings and appreciates them, one is free of fear.', 63441, 0), (458808, 'I think it matters whether someone has a good heart.', 10864, 0), (458809, 'Good leaders must communicate vision clearly, creatively, and continually. However, the vision doesn''t come alive until the leader models it.', 1810, 0), (458810, 'Among a great many other things that chess teaches you is to control the initial excitement you feel when you see something that looks good. It trains you to think before grabbing and to think just as objectively when you''re in trouble.', 7875, 0), (458811, 'You have to be very, very good looking to get ahead in motion pictures.', 56664, 0), (458812, 'The secret of a good sermon is to have a good beginning and a good ending, then having the two as close together as possible.', 1643, 0), (458813, 'Self-awareness is the ability to take an honest look at your life without any attachment to it being right or wrong, good or bad.', 5671, 0), (458814, 'I once had a rose named after me and I was very flattered. But I was not pleased to read the description in the catalogue: no good in a bed, but fine up against a wall.', 141, 0), (458815, 'I think every girl has a little bit of rebellion inside. It''s always fun to not follow every trend and not be the perfect good girl. It''s edgy to be a little rebellious.', 72271, 0), (458816, 'I''m a pretty good winner. I''m a terrible loser. And I rub it in pretty good when I win.', 66949, 0), (458817, 'Mankind is not likely to salvage civilization unless he can evolve a system of good and evil which is independent of heaven and hell.', 521, 0), (458818, 'It is no good to try to stop knowledge from going forward. Ignorance is never better than knowledge.', 30801, 0), (458819, 'Good things do not come easy. The road is lined with pitfalls.', 73015, 0), (458820, 'Teamwork is so important that it is virtually impossible for you to reach the heights of your capabilities or make the money that you want without becoming very good at it.', 697, 0), (458821, 'If there''s one thing I''m good at, it''s gathering people together to do something fun.', 22301, 0), (458822, 'My folks were raised pure prohibitionist. They were very good people, with high moral standards - but very repressed. There was no hugging and kissing in my home.', 38121, 0), (458823, 'Uncertainty is a very good thing: it''s the beginning of an investigation, and the investigation should never end.', 73016, 0), (458824, 'Simplicity is not the goal. It is the by-product of a good idea and modest expectations.', 19771, 0), (458825, 'But the real secret to lifelong good health is actually the opposite: Let your body take care of you.', 1194, 0), (458826, 'A person is born with feelings of envy and hate. If he gives way to them, they will lead him to violence and crime, and any sense of loyalty and good faith will be abandoned.', 46458, 0), (458827, 'I like to encourage people to realize that any action is a good action if it''s proactive and there is positive intent behind it.', 1856, 0), (458828, 'If it''s a good idea, go ahead and do it. It''s much easier to apologize than it is to get permission.', 73017, 0), (458829, 'Honesty and integrity are absolutely essential for success in life - all areas of life. The really good news is that anyone can develop both honesty and integrity.', 1692, 0), (458830, 'Life consists not in holding good cards but in playing those you hold well.', 3355, 0), (458831, 'My idea of a good night out is staying in.', 13073, 0), (458832, 'My philosophy of leadership is to surround myself with good people who have ability, judgment and knowledge, but above all, a passion for service.', 72215, 0), (458833, 'A conservative is a man with two perfectly good legs who, however, has never learned how to walk forward.', 2261, 0), (458834, 'The conscience of children is formed by the influences that surround them their notions of good and evil are the result of the moral atmosphere they breathe.', 62538, 0), (458835, 'A real man loves and respects his wife and is not only a good father but a man that his kids want to call ''Daddy.''', 68352, 0), (458836, 'The most important thing, in anything you do, is always trying your hardest, because even if you try your hardest and it''s not as good as you''d hoped, you still have that sense of not letting yourself down.', 20849, 0), (458837, 'A man is as good as he has to be, and a woman as bad as she dares.', 4, 0), (458838, 'Not only must we be good, but we must also be good for something.', 1049, 0), (458839, 'When I''m good, I''m very good. But when I''m bad I''m better.', 978, 0), (458840, 'All human beings are commingled out of good and evil.', 449, 0), (458841, 'The good old days are now.', 1046, 0), (458842, 'Better is the enemy of good.', 808, 0), (458843, 'He who stops being better stops being good.', 3851, 0), 